snippet.textDisplay: I haven't played this game but I know it's actually a good entry in the Sonic franchise, which is always good to hear after all the failed attempts. Sonic Generations is looking pretty nice as well, I admit I'm mostly interested in the Classic gameplay over the Modern gameplay from the videos I've seen. That and I can't wait to check out the soundtrack, that Green Hill Zone remix sounded nice.
